### Get offers by GTIN
GET http://localhost:3000/api/offers?gtin=4011700740086

###

### Update offers for a product (fetches from Qogita API)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/offers/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gtin": "4011700740086"
}

###

### Update offers for another product
POST http://localhost:3000/api/offers/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gtin": "4011700740123"
}

###

### Test with invalid GTIN (should return 404)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/offers/update
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "gtin": "9999999999999"
}

###

### Test with missing GTIN (should return 400)
POST http://localhost:3000/api/offers/update
Content-Type: application/json

{}

###
